## ğŸ§ª Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/jobify.git
cd jobify
````

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
# or
yarn install
```

### 3. Start the development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

## ğŸ“¦ Build

To create a production build:

```bash
